act/\">Claim Limited Offer</a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"plan\">\n<span class=\"tag\">Special Offer</span>\n<h3>Multi-Boutique</h3>\n<span class=\"price-badge\">\u2605 Special Offer \u2014 Save \u00a351</span>\n<div class=\"price\"><span class=\"was\">\u00a3200</span>\u00a3149 <small>initial setup</small></div>\n<div class=\"offer-save\">Limited-time offer \u00b7 normally \u00a3200</div>\n<div class=\"muted\" style=\"margin:-.1rem 0 .1rem;font-size:1rem\">then \u00a326 per month <span style=\"opacity:.8\">or \u00a3285 billed annually</span></div>\n<p class=\"muted\" style=\"margin:.5rem 0 0\">Designed for growing bridal businesses with up to three shops or locations.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Everything included in Single Boutique</li>\n<li>Up to three boutique locations</li>\n<li>Manage every location from one dashboard</li>\n<li>Separate staff and availability for each shop</li>\n<li>Location-specific services and opening hours</li>\n<li>Centralised booking management</li>\n<li>Priority email support</li>\n<li>Personal setup and onboarding</li>\n</ul>\n<a class=\"btn btn-gold\" href=\"/contact/\">Claim Limited Offer</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"container center\" style=\"margin-top:34px\">\n<p class=\"muted\">One straightforward setup fee and one monthly care plan. No commission, no per-booking charges and no unexpected platform fees.</p>\n</div>\n</section>"}, "elements": []}], "isInner": false}, {"id": "7ea70a4", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "full", "flex_direction": "column", "flex_align_items": "center", "background_background": "classic", "padding": {"unit": "px", "top": "78", "right": "20", "bottom": "78", "left": "20", "isLinked": false}, "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [], "column": "0", "row": "0"}, "background_color": "#EEF1E7"}, "elements": [{"id": "e0470d9", "elType": "container", "settings": {"content_width": "boxed", "flex_direction": "column", "flex_align_items": "center", "flex_gap": {"unit": "px", "size": 0, "sizes": [